AllPrintings.description: The file containing all cards, including all printings and variations, categorized by set.

AllPrintingsCSVFiles.description: The file containing a directory of .csv files containing all data from AllPrintings.json.

AllDeckFiles.description: The file containing all pre-constructed decks, compressed.

AllPrices.description: The file containing all prices of cards in various formats.

AllSetFiles.description: The file containing each individual set file in a directory, compressed.

Atomic.description: The file containing every card as a unique "atomic" object.

AttributeValues.description: The file containing known property values for data models.

CardTypes.description: The file containing every card type of any type of card.

CompiledList.description: The file containing all possible compiled outputs from MTGJSON, such as, AllPrintings, TypesCards, etc.

DeckList.description: The file containing all possible compiled pre-constructed deck outputs from MTGJSON.

Keywords.description: The file containing a list of all keywords used on Magic cards.

Legacy.description: The file containing all sets, restricted to sets legal in the Legacy format.

LegacyAtomic.description: The file containing all cards, restricted to cards legal in the Legacy format.

Meta.description: The file containing the metadata object, has {{link@ISO 8601@https://www.iso.org/iso-8601-date-and-time-format.html}} dates for latest build and prices, and version properties of this MTGJSON release.

PauperAtomic.description: The file containing all cards, restricted to cards legal in the Pauper format.

Pioneer.description: The file containing all sets, restricted to sets legal in the Pioneer format.

PioneerAtomic.description: The file containing all cards, restricted to cards legal in the Pioneer format.

Modern.description: The file containing all sets, restricted to sets legal in the Modern format.

ModernAtomic.description: The file containing all cards, restricted to cards legal in the Modern format.

SetList.description: The file containing a list of codes, names and release dates of all sets.

Standard.description: The file containing all sets, restricted to sets legal in the Standard format.

StandardAtomic.description: The file containing all cards, restricted to cards legal in the Standard format.

Vintage.description: The file containing all sets, restricted to sets legal in the Vintage format.

VintageAtomic.description: The file containing all cards, restricted to cards legal in the Vintage format.
